----------------------------------------------------------------------------

This project vendors the FT8/FT4 decoder/encoder in `crates/modes`, whose
algorithms were ported from the MIT-licensed `ft8_lib` (Kārlis Goba) and whose
protocol constant tables follow the WSJT-X (Franke/Taylor) on-air spec. See
`crates/modes/ATTRIBUTION.md` and `crates/modes/THIRD_PARTY_LICENSES/` for the
required attribution, which must travel with any distributed build.
